original: Forssell, Nils Fredrik, kyrkoherde, Totsö, f. 25/9/99 i Gbg. G. 27 m. Dagny Schmidt. Barn: Yvonne f. 28, Bengt 31. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 19, teol. fil. ex. 21, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Skara stift 25. Tjg. s. v. pastor i Fägre samt s. kommin. i Ransberg, kyrkoh. i Torsö sed. 41.
translated: Forssell, Nils Fredrik, clergyman, Totsö, born on September 25, 1899 in Gothenburg. Married in 1927 to Dagny Schmidt. Children: Yvonne (born in 1928) and Bengt (born in 1931). He graduated from high school in Gothenburg in 1919, received a degree in theology in 1921, passed practical theology exams and was ordained as a priest in Skara diocese in 1925. He served as a vicar in Fägre and a curate in Ransberg, and has been the pastor of Torsö since 1941.
